{"tid":1913310,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"呢條片望落IZONE班囡囡都幾好身材","createTime":"2020-03-06T16:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T02:38:18.000Z","uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca2d225c7322f6f17ada18fed96871ecda0fe61","tid":1913310,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GsEo4_9mIMg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGsEo4_9mIMg&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnKC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=b4f0dea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GsEo4_9mIMg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有幾個平時包得密密實實<br />\n估唔到都幾有料..."},{"pid":"d3f1791edc723d60d343d95625c139585e7d450e","tid":1913310,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:31:47.000Z","msg":"未分真假<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"